| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0507 — Recovery Inhibition (funksec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 01b54a06-75c6-516a-8c4b-badc5c8ac3d7"
